
 - to provide a program by which the mechanics of video editing can
   be separated from the contents of the video being edited

 - to make it easy to composite multiple video sequences into a final
   video

 - to make it easy to composite multiple audio clips into a final video

 - to provide a framework to support complex mappings of source to
   target image mappings

 - to do the above with the support of easily parallelizable rendering
   engines
